      "text": [
        " الَّذِي يَأْتِي الْبَهِيمَةَ فَيُولِجُ قَالَ عَلَيْهِ الْحَدُّ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Muhammad Bin Isa, from Yunus, from Ibn Muskan, from Abu Baseer, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> regarding the one who goes to the animals, so he penetrates. He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘Upon him is the Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>)’."
        ]
